    <h2>Overview</h2>
    <p>HelloDeploy uses only cookies and browser storage that are necessary to provide authentication, session security, CSRF protection, and user interface preferences. We do not use advertising cookies, cross-site tracking cookies, analytics cookies, or marketing pixels.</p>

    <h2>Cookies We Use</h2>
    <table class="table">
      <thead>
        <tr><th scope="col">Name</th><th scope="col">Purpose</th><th scope="col">Duration</th><th scope="col">Type</th></tr>
      </thead>
      <tbody>
        <tr>
          <td><code>hellodeploy.sid</code></td>
          <td>Maintains your authenticated session and connects requests to server-side session state.</td>
          <td>24 hours of inactivity, sign-out, or session destruction</td>
          <td>Strictly necessary</td>
        </tr>
      </tbody>
    </table>

    <h2>Browser Storage</h2>
    <table class="table">
      <thead>
        <tr><th scope="col">Key</th><th scope="col">Purpose</th><th scope="col">Duration</th><th scope="col">Type</th></tr>
      </thead>
      <tbody>
        <tr>
          <td><code>hd-theme</code></td>
          <td>Remembers your light or dark theme preference on the same browser.</td>
          <td>Until you clear browser storage or change preference</td>
          <td>Preference storage</td>
        </tr>
      </tbody>
    </table>

    <h2>Consent</h2>
    <p>The session cookie is strictly necessary to provide the service you request after signing in. Because HelloDeploy does not currently set optional analytics, advertising, or tracking cookies, there is no optional cookie category to accept or reject.</p>

    <h2>Managing Cookies</h2>
    <p>You can block or delete cookies in your browser settings. If you block the session cookie, you will not be able to sign in or use authenticated HelloDeploy features.</p>

    <h2>Changes</h2>
    <p>If HelloDeploy adds analytics, marketing, or other optional cookies in the future, this policy will be updated and a consent control will be added before those cookies are set where required.</p>

    <h2>Contact</h2>
    <p>Questions about cookies: <strong>hensonsagorsor@gmail.com</strong></p>
